          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Farmer Flexibility Act </b></p> <p>This bill extends the final planting date established by the Risk Management Agency for certain federal crop insurance policies covering grain sorghum. To account for extreme weather conditions, the final planting date for policies with an existing date of April 5, 2015, is extended to April 26, 2015. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-03-24T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
